'''Scimitar Stall''' is a unique stall found on [[Ape Atoll]]. It is owned by [[Daga]], the only person to sell a [[Dragon Scimitar]] in his store - [[Daga's Scimitar Smithy]]. Players with level 65 [[Thieving]] can steal from this stall roughly every 40 seconds, but this is risky due to the [[monkey archer]]s, [[Padulah]] and other surrounding dangers unless the player has completed [[Monkey Madness II]].

